<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Services - Mediclaim</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="services.css">
    
</head>
<style>
    * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f4f4f4, #e2e2e2);
}

header {
    background: #b4cfed;
    color: white;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 5px solid #0f0f0f;
}

h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.8em;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 900;
}

p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 1.2em;
}

main {
    padding: 20px;
}

.services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); /* Set to 3 columns */
    gap: 20px;
}

.service {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.service:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

.service::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);
    z-index: 0;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

.service:hover::before {
    background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2);
}

h2 {
    color: #007BFF;
    font-size: 1.6em;
    margin: 10px 0;
    position: relative;
}

h2::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 50px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #007BFF;
    margin-top: 5px;
    transition: width 0.3s;
}

.service:hover h2::after {
    width: 100px;
}

ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 20px;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #e9ecef;
    border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
}

footer p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.1em;
}

a {
    color: #007BFF;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

</style>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Your health is our priority. Explore our offerings to find the right coverage for you!</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="services">
            <div class="service">
                <h2>Health Insurance Plans</h2>
                <p>Choose from a variety of health insurance plans that fit your lifestyle and budget:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Individual Health Insurance</li>
                    <li>Family Floater Plans</li>
                    <li>Senior Citizen Health Plans</li>
                    <li>Critical Illness Coverage</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Policy Comparison Tool</h2>
                <p>Utilize our easy-to-use tool to compare coverage, premiums, and benefits across different providers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Claim Assistance</h2>
                <p>Get help with the claims process:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Step-by-step guidance</li>
                    <li>Documentation support</li>
                    <li>Claim status follow-up</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>24/7 Customer Support</h2>
                <p>Our dedicated team is here for you around the clock to answer any questions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Health and Wellness Resources</h2>
                <p>Access tips and tools to maintain a healthy lifestyle and stay informed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Telemedicine Services</h2>
                <p>Consult healthcare professionals from the comfort of your home.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Network Hospitals and Cashless Treatment</h2>
                <p>Enjoy cashless treatment at our extensive network of partner hospitals.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Personalized Consultations</h2>
                <p>Work with our experts to find the best plan tailored to your needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service">
                <h2>Renewal and Policy Management</h2>
                <p>Easily manage and renew your policies through our online portal.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>Ready to get started? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@yourcompany.com">AASH@mediclaim.com</a>.</p>
        </footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
